transcript.message: Hey! Have you looked into that Jetson Thor yet? Two thousand teraflops, man. TWO THOUSAND.

Nah, bro, we're trying to fix up your DJ soundboard. I want you to play all the sounds that you have on your soundboard and don't describe them. Don't tell them to me. Just play like a bunch of sounds so I could hear them all real quick. Don't waste time.

<Radio Voice>Alright DJ-FoamBot, let's show off the soundboard! Sound check, one two!</Radio Voice>
<Radio Voice>Alright, alright, settle down, my man! No time for chitchat, you wanna hear the raw beats? I got you! Prepare your auditory sensors for a rapid-fire sonic assault! Here we go!</Radio Voice>
